{"tid":893915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛機載逾2000公斤榴槤 乘客頂唔順拒起飛","createTime":"2018-11-08T04:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T04:47:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4190f404509b236ab433bd47d8c7ef7802f6f4e9","tid":893915,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541588343_56bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541588343_56bb.jpg&h=7c3beb11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼三佛齊航空（Sriwijaya）公司一班航機發生罕見事故，由於機上運載大量榴槤，機艙飄滿「香味」引起乘客不滿鼓譟，要求客機卸貨，更有乘客幾乎跟機組人員發生衝突，經過幾番父涉後，最終航空公司讓步，暫停起飛卸下榴槤。<br />\n涉事航班周一原定由北明古魯（Bengkulu）飛往耶加達飛機，但由於機艙內運載了2,025公斤（4,455磅）榴槤，乘客投訴機艙內充斥令人難忍的氣味，乘客齊達內（Amir Zidane）在facebook發文講述事發經過，「當我踏入機艙，我已嗅到榴槤的氣味，我向機艙人員投訴，但他們竟要求我填表投訴。」機艙人員更稱，飛機起飛後，氣味很快便會消散。<br />\n「我向其他乘客大喊『哪一位想飛機起飛？』﹐他們都重複說『我們不想！！』」其他乘客隨即亦開始投訴，有人幾乎「與機艙人員有肢體衝突」。最後航空公司要求乘客下機，安排卸下貨物。<br />\n三佛齊航空發言人強調，航空公司有權運送榴槤，「貨物只要根據飛行條例正確包裹及數量不超出限制，運送榴槤並不違法，很多航空公司都這樣做。」<br />\n北明古魯機場發言人證實，當時機上有2,025公斤榴槤，強調機場日後會評估包裝程序，以免令「乘客不適」。飛機原定11時40分啟程，結果延了1小時才起飛。<br />\n英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"f6ba62c012e7fd2bfaeaaa3025f34959886addd6","tid":893915,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"不知幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99b36728882ab43bf032877e347996f2d88c810","tid":893915,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba07b74c2b1d4fc160e87a6eb2d611e8036533a","tid":893915,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ce5327c55f247425788435bc77c17ce3e1e683","tid":893915,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"香港人，表示唔好阻住返工"},{"pid":"0a83aa437933839f73fd13734bbc0304566f52e3","tid":893915,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"經過幾番<span style=\"color: red;\">父</span>涉後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030e5ffa85a46b04eb574919169be7af5e9f7990","tid":893915,"uid":143105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"有得聞無得食真係好慘"},{"pid":"475e427dfc78343fa14dcb305590c1fb613ccc6a","tid":893915,"uid":73,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"延誤一小時算快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}